### 1. 用户登录（获取Token）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "zcjy",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token);
%}

### 2. 初始化所有区域的POI数据
POST http://localhost:8080/api/regions/init-all
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 3. 初始化指定区域的POI数据（例如：区域ID为1）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/regions/init/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 4. 查询所有省份
GET http://localhost:8080/api/regions/provinces
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 5. 查询指定省份的城市
GET http://localhost:8080/api/regions/cities?province=福建省
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 6. 查询省市的POI列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/regions/pois?province=福建省&city=龙岩市
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
